Add 3.0.0-r100 non-keyworded revision to build app-doc/cantera-3.0.0
with addditional build dependensies that aren't in ::gentoo:

dev-python/pint-0.23
dev-python/pydata-sphinx-theme-0.13.3-r1 (from ::gentoo history)

The app-text/doxygen-1.9.8 and dev-python/sphinxcontrib-katex-0.9.9
are also used.

Some objects.inv files are tried to download during build of Sphinx
documentation therefore it are added as additional SRC_URI items.

The cantera-docs-3.0.0_modify_menu.patch is iused to simplify
local documantation navigation.
